descriptions.chunkcacher: A Minecraft Fabric mod that caches chunk information to speed up world generation.
descriptions.tabfocus: Implement button focus by press tab feature in pre-1.9
descriptions.anchiale: Adds a faster way to exit worlds in 1.8. Use the menu.quitWorld button to exit the current world without waiting for the server tasks queue to complete.
descriptions.fastreset: Skips saving worlds to reset faster.
descriptions.statsperworld: Separation of achievements and statistics per world in Minecraft Pre-1.7
descriptions.z-buffer-fog: Legacy Fabric mod that make terrain fog rendering to planar
descriptions.biomethreadlocalfix: Fix Minecraft Biome ThreadLocal Memory leak issue
descriptions.antigone: Fixes a rare server deadlock in Minecraft 1.16.1
